  <official_title>A Double-blind Placebo Controlled, Randomized, Phase II Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability, Pharmacokinetics and Efficacy of Twice Daily Topical Applications of AP611074 5% Gel for up to 16 Weeks in Condyloma Patients</official_title>
