  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a double-blind placebo controlled, randomized, phase 2 study to assess the safety,
      tolerability, pharmacokinetics and efficacy of twice daily topical applications of AP611074
      5% Gel for up to 16 weeks in condyloma patients
    </textblock>
